item.title: ~Project Galaxy~ Discussion
item.dc:creator: @TheCyberMan TheCyberMan
item.description:
@TheCyberMan wrote:

[quote=“reyx7, post:15, topic:409215”][quote author=ziplock link=topic=510493.msg3705264#msg3705264 date=1312995627]

You are… Remaking the cache? What does that mean?

All of the item will look different, all of the gfx will be different, the landscape, the textures. It’s like a texture pack for runescape.

What about all the models? That’s the cache too.

The models are the items and the landscape. So are the gfx.

Soo… They will recreating every single one of the thousands of models…
[/quote]
It’s a 317 cache. There’s about 6500 inventory based items alone.[/quote]

So basically, models that have Runescape Classic graphics would probably be accepted. We just need to remake every model we can. Then in the future, we can work on improving the looks. Though, crappy and decent models mixed together is definitely acceptable.

About the thread “spam” problem: This is a place for people to talk about what ~Project Galaxy~ is, ask questions, see if they’re interested, etc. without having to just PM me. The members will post their development stuff on the actual thread itself.

Read full topic
